  "title": "Freshly Oven-Roasted Ukrainian Fish Borscht",
  "description": "A hearty, comforting fish borscht from Ukraine, featuring freshly roasted fish, a variety of vegetables, and a hint of lemon.",
  "cuisine": "Ukrainian",
