  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season the halibut fillets with salt and pepper.",
    "Sear the halibut in a hot skillet with olive oil until golden brown on both sides.",
    "Transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and roast the fish for 8-10 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "While the fish is cooking, chop the beets, carrots, and onion.",
    "In a large pot, combine the fish stock, water, chopped vegetables, and minced garlic.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 10-12 minutes, or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the roasted fish to the pot and stir in lemon juice.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the fish borscht hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
  ],
